!! Go Package commands

List all packages in Workspace:

```shell
go list ./...
```

List all packages avaliable:

```shell
go list ...
```


!! Documentation

`godoc` is not builtin since version 1.13.

```bash
go get golang.org/x/tools/cmd/godoc
```

Open documentation localhost.

```bash
godoc -http :8000
```

`gogetdoc`:

```bash
go get github.com/zmb3/gogetdoc
```

!! Go Debugger

```shell
go get -u github.com/go-delve/delve/cmd/dlv
```

!! Go Linting

